Meta.DisplayName=Redis (ATLAS Database)
Meta.Description=Runs the ATLAS Redis database as its own AMP instance, so the whole ATLAS setup can be managed and started from within AMP. After creating the instance, copy the files from your ATLAS instance's AtlasTools\RedisDatabase folder into this instance's Redis folder, then Start.
